    <h2>A free social network for keeping in touch with humans.</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>No wall of endless shit. No algorithms. No advertisements or promoted content.</li>
      <li>Add friends, family, colleagues, people you meet on the road, like any other social network.</li>
      <li>Pin people to your homepage to only see updates from the people you really want to see updates from. You can look up the others when you feel like it.</li>
      <li>End-to-end encryption means only the people you connect with can read your posts. Not even admins.</li>
      <li>100% open source and decentralised. Host your own version and stay in touch with people on other networks.</li>
    </ul>

